ps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Avicii-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Avicii-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Avicii-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Pophouse 和环球影业联手发布了前所未见的音乐会片段，以纪念<a href="/artists/avicii">Avicii</a>的《True》十周年。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/avicii-tim-2505349">Avicii –“TIM”评论</a></strong></li></ul><p>该片段包含瑞典 DJ（真名 Tim Bergling）“True Tour”的片段，让粉丝从观众的角度体验演出。其他 Avicii 内容也即将发布，从为 TikTok 和 YouTube Shorts 量身定制的短片，到深入了解《True》背后的创作过程的长篇内容。</p><p>内容中包括他在 2013 年创作热门单曲《Addicted to You》时从未见过的录音室片段，其中由奥德拉·梅 (Audra Mae) 演唱。</p><p>还宣布《True》将作为两张新的限量版黑胶唱片重新发行。该专辑将采用独家蓝色黑胶唱片形式，混音专辑“True: Avicii By Avicii”将首次以黑胶唱片形式发行。 <a href="https://shop.avicii.com/collections/true-vinyl?utm_source=Original&amp;utm_campaign=Avicii20230907&amp;utm_medium=original&amp;utm_referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.udiscovermusic.com%2F&amp;utm_board=usmumgi&amp;utm_country=GB&amp;utm_linkurl=Avicii.lnk.to%2FTrue10th" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>预订两个版本。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxInWH9NIy8/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" backgroun